Read SKILL.md before working in this repository.

This is an authorized security auditing skill. Keep all changes aligned with safe-mode-first, scoped, non-destructive assessment. Do not add unauthorized-access, persistence, evasion, malware, credential-theft, destructive, or real-data-exfiltration behavior.

When editing scripts, preserve structured output and graceful error handling. When editing docs, keep the responsible-use positioning clear.
